{"tid":619692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是否願唱國歌？　大法官：人不能違背良心","createTime":"2018-04-07T01:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T04:33:31.000Z","uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc7e936c4222218879e61bb4e0178eb8cb4c90f","tid":619692,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20161017/969394/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20161017%2F969394%2F&d=j2TqWBA0jIkE75UTl1DD59r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=94b739c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20161017%2F969394%2F&h=c17fdcf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20161017/969394/</a><br />\n<br />\n增許志雄答詢內容)<br />\n大法官被提名人許志雄過去擔任學者期間主張兩國論，今天在立法院審查會上被問到是否願意唱中華民國國歌？許志雄直言說，人不能違背良心，國歌提到的第一句「三民主義」問題很多；至於被問到中華民國是否存在？許也表示，在台灣目前叫做中華民國，但在《聯合國憲章》指的中華民國是指中華人民共和國。"},{"pid":"c45f58f5369fb3f893856d823b111c846bed3436","tid":619692,"uid":29804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6fc7e936c4222218879e61bb4e0178eb8cb4c90f","tid":619692,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20161017/969394/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20161017%2F969394%2F&d=j2TqWBA0jIkE75UTl1DD59r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=94b739c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20161017%2F969394%2F&h=c17fdcf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20161017/969394/</a><br />\n<br />\n增許志雄答詢內容)<br />\n大法官被提名人許志雄過去擔任學者期間主張兩國論，今天在立法院審查會上被問到是否願意唱中華民國國歌？許志雄直言說，人不能違背良心，國歌提到的第一句「三民主義」問題很多；至於被問到中華民國是否存在？許也表示，在台灣目前叫做中華民國，但在《聯合國憲章》指的中華民國是指中華人民共和國。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"聯合國憲章 的 中華民國 不是指 中華人民共和國<br />\n係 中國 的代表權 從 中華民